Text: Marty Stuart eller Marty Robbins... det är frågan :) Titlarna säger mig 'Robbins', så det kanske vore läge att ändra i titeln? :)

I think the previous comment says that this should be labelled as Marty Robbins, not as Marty Stuart.  Two different but amazing country artists - I love them both, but there is definitely a difference!
